---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Careers - The Davinci Project" description="Join our team and help build the future of digital asset transfers.">
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Careers</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Join our team and help build the future of digital asset transfers.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="content-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Why Join Us?</h2>
      <p>The Davinci Project is at the forefront of digital asset transfer technology. We're building a protocol that provides trust, security, and reliability in the world of cryptocurrency.</p>
      <p>We're looking for talented individuals who are passionate about blockchain technology and want to make a real impact in the financial world.</p>
      
      <h2>Open Positions</h2>
      <div class="positions-list">
        <div class="position-item">
          <h3>Senior Blockchain Developer</h3>
          <p>We're looking for an experienced blockchain developer to help build and maintain our escrow protocol.</p>
          <span class="position-type">Full-time · Remote</span>
        </div>
        <div class="position-item">
          <h3>Security Engineer</h3>
          <p>Help us ensure the highest levels of security for our protocol and user assets.</p>
          <span class="position-type">Full-time · Remote</span>
        </div>
        <div class="position-item">
          <h3>Product Manager</h3>
          <p>Lead the development and strategy of our product offerings.</p>
          <span class="position-type">Full-time · Remote</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
      <p>Don't see a position that matches your skills? We're always interested in hearing from talented individuals. Send your resume and a brief introduction to <a href="mailto:careers@davinciproject.net">careers@davinciproject.net</a></p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    padding: 8rem 0 4rem;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--bg-primary) 0%, var(--bg-secondary) 100%);
  }
  
  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }
  
  h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }
  
  .subtitle {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    max-width: 600px;
  }
  
  .content-section {
    padding: 4rem 0;
  }
  
  .content-section h2 {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }
  
  .content-section p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    max-width: 800px;
  }
  
  .content-section a {
    color: var(--accent-green);
  }
  
  .positions-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }
  
  .position-item {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    transition: border-color 0.3s;
  }
  
  .position-item:hover {
    border-color: var(--accent-green);
  }
  
  .position-item h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }
  
  .position-item p {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  .position-type {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--accent-green);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .page-hero {
      padding: 7rem 0 3rem;
    }
    
    h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
    
    .container {
      padding: 0 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>
